data.description: Gorgeous historic home in Founder's Place! Come and sit down in the lovely spacious living room, with two original built in book cases with seating. Have a nice dinner in the grand formal dining room, perfect for entertaining and holiday gatherings! One and a half bathrooms have been updated. Beautiful original woodwork throughout this high ceiling, delightful home. Enjoy the sunrise or night fall on the large front or back porch for a nice breeze, or hangout inside with the 2 brand new HVAC Units. Fun Fact - There's a hidden secret staircase. So much character and charm, possibilities are endless with this home!
